(area_cell_area, area_cell_area).explanation: A variable cannot have a causal relationship with itself as it represents the same physical measurement;

(area_cell_area, time).explanation: Cell area is a static physical design parameter that does not directly influence execution or simulation time;

(area_cell_area, area_net_area).explanation: Both represent independent area components in chip design where cell area and net routing area are determined by different design constraints and do not directly cause each other;
